textfsm_template:
Value INTERFACE (\S+)
Value INDEX (\d+)
Value SNMP_INDEX (\d+)
Value FLAGS (.+)
Value ENCAPSULATION (\S+)
Value INPUT_PACKETS (\d+)
Value OUTPUT_PACKETS (\d+)

Start
  ^Logical interface ${INTERFACE} \(Index ${INDEX}\) \(SNMP ifIndex ${SNMP_INDEX}\)
  ^\s+Flags: ${FLAGS}\s+Encapsulation: ${ENCAPSULATION}
  ^\s+Input packets\s*:\s*${INPUT_PACKETS}
  ^\s+Output packets\s*:\s*${OUTPUT_PACKETS} -> Record
